casebody.head_matter:
James E. WHITNEY, petitioner,
v.
Cindy GLOVER, Clerk, Circuit Court of Lincoln County, Arkansas, et al.
No. 18-6736.
Supreme Court of the United States
Jan. 22, 2019.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
